MID_支援_ニュクス_ハロルド_Ｃ: $t1$Wmニュクス|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsニュクス|$WaWhere are you going, Harold?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaOh, Nyx. I'm going to see a\nshow with the kids in town.$k$p$Eキメ,|All the parents are busy so they\nasked me to go in their steed.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|Is that so? How considerate.$k$p$Eキメ,|But you shouldn't go.\nSomething bad will happen.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Something bad?\nOn what grounds?$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E通常,|My fortune telling.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Fortune telling?$k$p$Eキメ,|Hahaha.$k$pEven though you went out of your way to\nwarn me, it's impossible for me to not go.$k$pWhat would I even say?\nI got a bad fortune telling so I can't go?$k$pSuch a reason wouldn't stand.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E苦,|I understand how you feel,\nbut I want you to trust me. Don't go.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,|Thank you for the warning.\nI'll be leaving then.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,|Wait. You can go then, but please\nput this underneath your armor.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Is this a magic manual?\nIt's pretty thick.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,|Enough. Just do as I say.\nIt will definitely be of use.$k
MID_支援_ニュクス_ハロルド_Ｂ: $t1$Wmニュクス|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|$w0|Nyx...\nAbout the other day, I'm really sorry...$k$pFor looking down on your fortune telling...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,|What happened? I want to know.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|After you spoke to me, I took the\nchildren to watch a magic show.$k$pThe magician's assistant\ngot into a wooden box...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E通常,|And you impale it with swords...\nIt's a common magic trick.$k$pUsually there's some sort\nof gimmick to the swords...$k$p$E苦,汗|But I managed to read the turn of events...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|As you had said, the magician selected\nme as an assistant from the crowd.$k$p$Eキメ,|Of course I got into the\nbox without complaints.$k$p$E苦,汗|...The sword wasn't a magic prop, but a\nreal sword which pierced through the box.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,汗|As I had predicted...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|I thought it was strange that\nmy armor had been pierced.$k$p$Eキメ,|However, I couldn't bring myself to\nsay anything in front of the children.$k$pPerhaps there was some kind of trick\nto it, so that I wouldn't get stabbed.$k$pAfter thinking about it,\nI decided to stay still.$k$p$E苦,汗|But then the sword pierced\nthrough my armor...$k$p$E通常2,|Just as I thought I was going to die,\nI was saved by your magic manual.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|Hehehe, that's why I told you.\nMy fortune telling is absolute.$k$pOn rare occasions,\nI can see others' futures clearly.$k$pYou must be a simple minded idi―$k$p$E怒,汗|...No, a person that's more\npure-hearted than any other.$k$p$E通常,|Usually it isn't good to change the future,\nbut you are my ally, so I gave you a warning.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|It was all thanks to you.$k$pBy the way, tonight's mission\nis to attend Elise's dinner.$k$pI'll be all right this time, yes?$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|Ehehe. You already completely\ntrust my fortune telling.$k$pBut as I said, it's not good\nto change the future.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Then you don't have to tell me anything\nspecific. Please, something vague will do.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,汗|…Well, it can't be helped.\nI'll have a look for you.$k$p$Eキメ,|…………$k$p$E笑,|...Hehehe.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|What's wrong?$k\n$Wsニュクス|Someone's going to going to get very\nangry at you, so please be careful.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Someone's going to get very angry at me?\nWhat could this mean...$k
MID_支援_ニュクス_ハロルド_Ａ: $t1$Wmニュクス|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|$w0|Haah...$k$pLady Elise got so mad at me.\nIt's just as Nyx had warned me.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|Oh my, let me hear the story.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|As expected, I arrived at\nthe dinner with Lady Elise.$k$pAt first, I was asked what I'd like to drink,\nso I replied with water.$k$pThen the drinks promptly arrived.$k$p$E通常,|I was pretty thirsty, so I drank all the water.$k$pHowever, that was...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|It wasn't water...but alcohol, correct?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Exactly! The waiters had made\na mistake and prepared alcohol.$k$p$E怒,汗|Even though I drank it all at once,\nI'm not good at holding my liquor.$k$pSoon after, everything became a blur...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,|It must have stirred up some trouble.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Indeed.$k$p$E通常,|It was when we had finished the appetizers\nand soup, and the bread came out.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E通常,|I see.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|In my vague consciousness,\nI got myself a piece of bread.$k$pThen when I tried to put it in my mouth...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,|What happened?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|It was...$k$pLady Elise's hair...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E笑,|I'm sure there are others out there who\nmust think her hair looks like bread...$k$pAhahaha...!$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa…………$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|Oh my... I laughed a bit too much.\n...My apologies.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|No, there's no need to apologize.$k$p$E苦,|In fact, seeing you laugh so hard\nmakes me feel a little bit better.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E苦,汗|I-is that so?$k$p$E通常,|...To be honest, I've come to enjoy telling\nyour future quite a bit as of late,$k$p$E笑,|since you keep getting into\nall these strange scenarios.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|I see.$k$p$E通常2,|Well if that's the case, I want you to laugh\nas much as you can at my misfortune.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaVery well. Leave it to me.$k
MID_支援_ニュクス_ハロルド_Ｓ: $t1$Wmニュクス|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsニュクス|$WaHarold, what's wrong?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaNyx, you came just in time.$k$p$E怒,|The truth is, I have something to ask you.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaSomething to ask me?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaI know this may be rude in consensus,\nbut I want to ask...$k$p$E苦,汗|...How old are you?$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E怒,|What will you do if I tell you?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaAh, well...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,|You don't have a reason then.\nOh well, I'll tell you.$k$p$E怒,|I may not look like it,\nbut I'm a lot older than you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Huh?!$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,|A long time ago, I spent too much\ntime practicing my art on the streets.$k$pAs a result, my body stopped aging.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|I-is that so...$k$p$E通常,|But if you're older then it's not a problem.\nYou looked so young that I...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E通常,|?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,|…………$k$p$E通常2,照|...I'll just say it.\nNyx, I want you to marry me.$k$p$Eキメ,照|This is the wedding ring.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$E通常,照|…………$k$p$E笑,照|...Thank you. I'm glad.\nI'll happily accept it.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|Oh! To think that I would receive\nsuch a good response so quickly!$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaThe truth is, I knew...that you\nwere going to propose today.$k$p$Eキメ,照|Because that's what my fortunes told me...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,照|Ah, I see.$k$pThat makes sense now that I think about it.$k$pThis means everything is going\nas you had predicted.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaYes.$k$p$E通常,照|When I first met you, I already\nknew about this day.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,照|Huh!?\nWhen you first met me!?$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,照|That's right.$k$p$E笑,照|I shouldn't change the future...$k$p...You understand the meaning\nof those words, right?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|Ahh.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,照汗|I didn't want you dying during the show,\nso I change the future a bit.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,照汗|W-well then, could I ask you something?\nWhat do you see...in our future together?$k\n$Wsニュクス|$Wa$Eキメ,照|…………$k$p$E笑,照|...I see a child.\nA cute child born from the both of us.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|That's wonderful...\nThat is a blessing to me...$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaMe, as well.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,照|I want to make you... happier\nthan you are now.$k\n$Wsニュクス|$WaThank you, but I knew that already, too.$k$pThe fact that you'll take good care of me,\nthe fact that you'll be a wonderful father...$k$p$Eキメ,照|...I knew it all already.$k
